    "description": "Join RepRally as a Commission Sales Representative. Sell to independent retail stores on your own schedule with uncapped earning potential. No interviews required — complete self-service onboarding and start selling immediately.\n\nWhat You'll Do\n\nSell RepRally's catalogue to independent retail stores in your area. Use the RepRally app to place orders and manage your accounts. Work on your own schedule with no quotas or minimum hours.\n\nWhat You Bring\n\nValid driver's license and reliable vehicle. Smartphone with a data plan. Self-motivated and comfortable working independently.\n\nWhy RepRally\n\n100% commission — you eat what you kill. No floor, no ceiling. Start immediately with self-service onboarding. Work when you want, where you want. Prove yourself and move into our stipend program with guaranteed weekly pay.",
